INSTALLATION

falcon <wuzj@lemote.com>
2009-08-15

1. Compile

use Debian/Linux as an example:

install these three -dev packages at first,

$ apt-get install libxext-dev libxft-dev libglib2.0-dev

compile:

$ make

2. Install

by default, the fnkey will be installed to /usr/bin, and the default.sh and
fnkey.conf will be copied to /etc/fnkey/

$ make install
